{"tid":2447110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：長者對科興疫苗卻步是文宣解說不足 安心監控未見成效","createTime":"2021-03-15T03:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T04:12:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1697f6311f762fdea3644158a1ece6643068b69c","tid":2447110,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"何栢良認為要利用精準數據釋除對接種疫苗疑慮<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在本台節目《千禧年代》，回應應否降低優先接種新冠疫苗年齡限制，他認為，接種計劃開展以來正有秩序進行，安排亦做得好，但近期巿民對於疫苗是否適合接種都產生混亂，而科興疫苗接種首10天已有不良反應報告，令60歲以上以及有長期病患者會擔心，認為疫苗資訊方面可以有所調節。 <br />\n<br />\n他認為，需要工作證明去接種疫苗帶來不便，取消相關要求相信會有更多人接種。至於科興疫苗，他認為，政府現時未有精準數據顯示巿民接種後，會否提高中風及心臟病發機會，他相信要利用精準數據分析才能釋除疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n另外，何栢良又說，暫時很難評論西營盤的Ursus Fitness群組爆發，是否已過頂峰，但認為今次情況，已較跳舞群組好。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，有關群組有過百人感染，涉及的人士亦有去過餐廳等場所，安心出行程式安裝人數增加，但似乎未見發揮功效，不排除這些餐廳會再有感染群組出現，但控制方面已較過往有進步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580626-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580626-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=95f290a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580626-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=348a31c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580626-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b2aefe0cc34b737ce1d58cf9125fccfcbd9f6cd7","tid":2447110,"uid":33939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"一個冇誠信嘅政府做乜都碌柒架啦"},{"pid":"bbb54b99fd872d7bf940fda413a31ff3a026cefb","tid":2447110,"uid":46388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"安心出行程式安裝人數增加，但似乎未見發揮功效<br />\n佢想有咩功效? 裝左就防毒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e9f3b53b4959980f2fc3a0617ac70788004fb9","tid":2447110,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"有啲死亡實例睇到，洗咩解說"},{"pid":"0f88f9e2bcfb71dc861f8f54b222ccc6a1c54226","tid":2447110,"uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"何栢良：長者對科興疫苗卻步<br />\n記者：咁你打左咩疫苗?<br />\n何栢良：......."},{"pid":"6ba609f18443439f3178032d825471ff6eb166e5","tid":2447110,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"許豎娼都打BioNTech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7743946ad5220b3123668a12b380f2c5febb07ac","tid":2447110,"uid":196222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"何總監，而家爭你咋，<br />\n打BNT學梁院長咪大方d照直認囉。"},{"pid":"b52d2f093319ae311e71fa13647b308d43e4f78e","tid":2447110,"uid":220766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"成日都解說解說<br />\n跟本政府已經冇人想理你 你講幾多都唔會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36972373924a0194f51903dd7e526a81d84c5679","tid":2447110,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7918ff2009fd82773fa6260e9b33eb10cd881b3e","tid":2447110,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔得嘅嘢無論分析幾多次都係唔得</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"31f63e3b36e95bc6d098b00ef808ebab789dcd5e","tid":2447110,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"咁你做咩唔打科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ef3def6e9bbf54a8f2790f4c0f37730aa0d759","tid":2447110,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy